</ol>


<h3 class="book">How We Use the Information We Collect</h3>

<p class="privacy book">We will never sell your Personal Information and, except as set forth below, will never share your Personal Information with any third parties.</p>

<ol class="first">
<li class="book"><strong>Connection Suggestions.</strong><br>
We may use your Personal Information to suggest contacts or connections you should make with other users (or other users should make with you) based on your relationships in your Dandelion address book.   However, we will only ever share the public user profile that any third party already has access to (as set by your privacy controls on such Third Party Website) and will never share the full profile that a user would only have access to if you were both connected on such Third Party Website.</li>
<li class="book"><strong>Internal Use.</strong><br>
We may also use your Personal Information to contact you about the Service, to personalize and improve the Service, and to analyze how users utilize the Service.</li>
<li class="book"><strong>External Use.</strong>

